  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '2. Original Gate (1983): Eleven''s Accidental Opening


    Eleven (Jane
    Ives/El) was the first to open the gate to the Upside Down at Hawkins Lab, doing
    so unintentionally on November 6, 1983. While using her powers in a sensory deprivation
    tank to make contact with a Demogorgon, she tore the fabric of reality, creating
    the "Mothergate". Dr. Brenner forced Eleven to make mental contact with the creature.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1c00b38d489a04f16b85be30d54ba97e, type: 2}
