  m_text: '3. Will''s Abduction (1983): The Demogorgon''s First Strike


    After
    Eleven created the Mothergate in 1983, the Upside Down''s influence grew rapidly,
    leading to the abduction of Will Byers by a Demogorgon. Eleven escaped, met Mike,
    Lucas, and Dustin, and helped them find Will, revealing the existence of the
    dark dimension.'
