  m_text: "4. Will's Possession & The Tunnels (1984): The Mind Flayer's Control\n\nWill,
    rescued but possessed by the Mind Flayer (under Vecna\u2019s control), heavily
    traumatized and mentally controlled by Vecna (Henry Creel), became a conduit
    for the Hive Mind, allowing Vecna to map out underground tunnels to expand his
    reach across Hawkins. Will's visions guided the creation of underground, vine-covered
    tunnels beneath Hawkins, spreading the Upside Down's influence."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1c00b38d489a04f16b85be30d54ba97e, type: 2}
